item.description:
Hello, I will NOT be able to attend this trivia (already going to another of our events at the same time), but I know that some group members enjoy going, so please look for the other group members at Firefly's. I will see you next week!

Join us for Stump Team Trivia at Firefly's in Framingham. Trivia starts at 7:30pm. We will meet at 7pm to get a spot. Join us for drinks, food and a fun time playing team trivia. Everyone is responsible for their own food/drink. If you have trouble finding us, please call Catherine at 774 232 0000.
item.how_to_find_us: Look for Catherine (see photo) If need to, please call 774 232 0000
item.name: Stump Team Trivia at Firefly's Framingham
